=20
percent rebate on their electricity bill. It is the watt hogs, who never=20
lowered the air conditioner and left lights burning all over their homes,=
=20
whose paltry efforts netted them the governor's award.=20
Give the governor credit for keeping the lights on in California. But his=
=20
less-than- bold decisions will result in serious political and economic=20
consequences. Soon, we will have to confront the grave reality that we have=
=20
mortgaged many of our dreams =01( for expanded health care, improved educat=
